<https://colonial-heritage.triply.cc/nmvw/id/object/RV-02-1085> <https://colonialcollections.nl/schema#inscription> "折葦江上客\r\n西來東渡人\r\n大意人人有\r\n空走徒勞心\r\n\r\nthe traveller on the river bends the reeds\r\nComing from the West is the one crossing towards the East\r\nEvery one knows the essence of truth\r\nWalking in vain is only to fatigue the heart" .
